Description: Access the United States National Provider Identifier
    Registry API (if available) and provide informative error messages
    when it's not. Obtain rich administrative data linked to a specific 
    individual or organizational healthcare provider, or perform advanced 
    searches based on provider name, location, type of service, credentials, 
    and many other attributes.
